    "body": "<!-- Checklist for requesting a feature:\r\n- Check the issue tracker. The feature you are requesting may have already been requested.\r\n- Check if the feature does not exist on the latest developer's version.\r\nI have checked and there are no issues related to this feature\r\n-->\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nIn  OnlineLibraryFragment  & PagerFragment  while scrolling the keyboard just stays there and takes so much space of the page\r\nwhich in my opinion isn't a great experience, its better if we scroll and the keyboard goes away :)\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nI will addOnScrollListener to the recycler view so everytime we scroll the keyboard gets hidden\r\n\r\n**Describe alternatives you've considered**\r\nif we use a touch listener, then the keyboard hiding code is called multiple times each second while scrolling, which is not efficient.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nBefore my approach \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/75211982/137470164-0d79d9d4-6856-4956-88b2-d8fcdc72a653.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\nAfter my approach \r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/75211982/137470182-efae0cbd-4e29-42df-bff1-d60632b8363f.mp4",
